Comment: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:10.86,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fnArial\b1\c&H4D4D4D&\3c&HD3D3D3&\shad0}Molesters Targeting Students on School Trips\NKyoto City on High Alert\N{\fs42\fnTimes New Roman\3c&HE8E8E8&} A high number of incidents of thefts, blackmail, and groping \Nin dense areas such as on buses, \Ncontinues to plague students on school trips in Kyoto.\NSuch incidents targeting students are particularly prevalent\Nin Kyoto, as compared to the rest of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:08.86,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:09.86,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Just you here, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.24,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.37,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Did you just put something in your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:17.12,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm preparing for the school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.16,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.50,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's coming up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:23.88,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Things aren't so great \Nbetween us right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,but hopefully the school trip \Nbrings us back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:29.13,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.39,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We can get back to how we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.40,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Underwear, socks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.27,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Are you bringing your own toothbrush?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Come on, Raiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.11,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We don't need to buy everything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:44.77,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,You have money saved up from tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.70,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,No one's going to blame you for \Nspending some of it on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.33,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,But the sisters are going to hate you \Nif you cheaped out on their birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.66,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Their birthday's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.91,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,It already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.42,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,They were late, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.63,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Besides, they never told me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.30,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,If you get something, you give back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:10.43,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Even elementary school kids know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:12.93,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Do you think I should get them something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.47,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.81,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I was texting with Itsuki{**-san} yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:20.81,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,We decided to come shopping together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Anyway, their birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.32,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.69,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} here with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:31.33,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,In that case, we can't shop together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:35.70,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I might know what to get them \Nif I watch how they shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.46,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:43.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We're shopping for the same trip anyway.\NWhat's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.33,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.59,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But while they may share a purpose, \Nthey're totally different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.34,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm here to buy underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.72,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,R-R-R-R-R-R-R-R-R-Raiha{**-chan},\Nwhat do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:58.26,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I think that's way too adult, I-Itsuki{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.68,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm a h-h-h-h-high schooler, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.23,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,This is about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.60,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't you need to shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:08.32,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I tend to take good care of my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You're still wearing little girl panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.99,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,H-How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.49,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:14.16,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.49,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Where's Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.74,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,She's taking her own measurements \Nand trying some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You're quintuplets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Couldn't she just buy the same sizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.29,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,That's quintuplet harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.55,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Quintassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:28.29,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I don't know why she's taking \Nmeasurements, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:33.17,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,She hasn't grown more \Nthan the rest of us, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.97,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I guess things are complicated \Nfor quintuplets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.60,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.39,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Especially these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:44.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,N-No, anyway, school camp \Nended pretty badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's make sure we don't regret \Nanything on our school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Not that I really care, but I'll \Nbe sure to take care of my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.61,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Sheesh. You act like you aren't \Nlooking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.62,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,He's been looking through the guidebook\Nover and over at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Raiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.00,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Besides, you might run into \Nthe girl from the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.71,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.17,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Huh? Wasn't that in Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.88,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,That's what Dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.42,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Even then, she was a tourist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What girl in the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.60,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Come on, you should show her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:17.89,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I don't even have the photo anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.14,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Something smells fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You should be able to tell me, \Nif it's actually nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.56,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I know why you can't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.23,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's because you have regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.61,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Now, tell me, and get it off your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She's a girl I ran into in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Her name is Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.20,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.45,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,The end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.58,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,B-But you've got me curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:48.58,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I want to hear a little more! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.34,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,She's basically his first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.46,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,F-First love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.51,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey! No one ever said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.48,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Full house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.73,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.74,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.32,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're playing one more game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.90,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'll take you on anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.03,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.99,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku, the game's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.04,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Two pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,So slow! And weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You seem sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.66,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I noticed you woke up early\Nand went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.42,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.92,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I begged my workplace to\Nlet me borrow the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:37.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So are you going to have him try it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.68,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You've worked so hard for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.14,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.39,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I hope it's still good when it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:52.31,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,How about the next person who wins \Ngets to ask anyone else to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.65,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.69,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:57.57,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.57,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.83,Italics,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,These sparks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.08,Italics,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We're just really into this card game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.46,Default,Sensei,0,0,0,,We'll have your large luggage\Ntaken to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.46,Default,Sensei,0,0,0,,Bring only your valuables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.59,Default,Sensei,0,0,0,,That's it for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.62,Default,Sensei,0,0,0,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.89,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.77,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,No, I think I just imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.98,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I wonder where Fu{**-kun}'s group is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Is there anywhere you all want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.11,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Well, if you're going to travel, \Nyou have to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Fancy shops are way more fun\Nthan some old temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.87,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.83,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We're in Kyoto, of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.87,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You want him to try\Nsome of the local delicacies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I agree with that too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, I'd like to remind him of\Nwhat happened that day here at this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.68,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I mean, we could go explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.13,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Itsuki, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.63,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.01,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}'s group left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.18,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,The only reason we wouldn't agree\Nto meet up with them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.31,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,is because we're all thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.34,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.91,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Do these go on forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.33,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I've seen pictures of them, \Nbut they're stunning in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.91,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,This is so grammable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.91,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone, peace signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.96,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's kind of rare that we get a \Npicture of just us sisters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.46,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, don't we have any of just the five of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.26,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Didn't we take one \Nat the fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:46.06,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We haven't taken one since we were\Non our field trip back in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's get a picture of \Nall of us this time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.10,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Do you think Futaro's at the top already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I haven't gotten a glimpse of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.23,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Guys are fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:57.36,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,All right, we need to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.11,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,This stairway's... pretty long... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.61,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,My legs are starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.61,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone! You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.87,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,She doesn't have a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.08,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That's what we love about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:11.99,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,She's nothing like a certain \Nschemer that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.79,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're coming up with some \Nnasty plan again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Me? I would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.42,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,There are two ways we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.68,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It looks like both lead to the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.60,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Which way has Fu{**-kun} gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.68,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I'll fall behind pretty badly \Nif I don't meet him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.82,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's already noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.98,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch at that shop over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.86,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Wait, lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Is there something else you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.24,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.32,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Full house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.20,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.75,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.50,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku and I will take the right route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:01.38,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Ichika, Nino, and Itsuki \Nwill take the left route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.67,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,That way, we'll run into \NUesugi{**-san} at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.88,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.34,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You can't decide that for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.09,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I am the victor! My orders are absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.81,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I have the right to order you to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:21.73,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look what happened because \Nof your stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.11,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Judging from the flow of people, \Nthe other route was the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.94,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.32,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.95,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's a washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.91,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:35.75,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I guess we took the right route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.08,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,There aren't any ahead, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I guess I should go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.26,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.39,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Hurry up, or lunchtime's going to be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.97,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.57,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You worked so hard for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Hang in there just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.57,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.23,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.36,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.28,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:14.20,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I wonder what Fu{**-kun}'s group \Nhad planned for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.74,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.75,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Where's Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.62,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.38,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,From what I saw on the map, \Nthis is the shorter route to the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.18,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I might not be able to beat \NYotsuba when she's by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:33.39,Italics,,0,0,0,,but given Miku's fitness,\NI should be able to beat them to the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.26,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,What do I do when I meet Futaro{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.64,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Those other guys will be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.65,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Still, Miku's been suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.40,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,She's going to make a move \Nsometime during this school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.15,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I have to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.65,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,If I can't take back the lie\NI've already told,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:55.66,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,all I can do is continue to lie \Nin order to stop Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.17,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.30,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,We didn't run into each other along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,which must mean Futaro{**-kun} \Ntook the right route.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.05,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.42,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I ran a lot. Miku and Yotsuba\Ncan't be here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.99,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.24,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed up as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.36,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,If there's a reason for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:39.49,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Ichika, this wasn't what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.00,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Is this what you really wanted to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.83,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.17,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Ichika's trying to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.88,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Get in the way of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.84,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,In the way of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.76,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.43,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,your confession to Uesugi{**-san}, Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.47,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay... I made it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.77,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.74,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, did you just hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.99,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.66,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're finally at the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.25,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.37,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.12,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika, you crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.96,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm getting fed up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.47,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Are you happy about making her cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.97,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Wait, Nino, that was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.89,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:46.23,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No matter the result... this is\Nmore or less what I was trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,How low are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:50.86,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:55.61,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You said at the hot springs that you \Nwould walk over anyone to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.95,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,How are we any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:58.86,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I don't intend on giving \Nhim up to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:09.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,But the bond between the five of us\Nis just as important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.13,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Even if you were the one \Nwho was chosen someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have wanted to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.55,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,I can't walk another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.18,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.14,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,you ate too much at the restaurant below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:26.90,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.44,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:31.15,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know what's going on, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:34.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Girls, take it down a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.32,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Shut up and stay out of this!\NYou'll make things even messier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Go chase after Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:39.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.54,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.54,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll meet you up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.50,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.04,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I-I'll go find her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.29,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're going down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.04,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Shit, Miku's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.81,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I got through to Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.44,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,She's on the bus with Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.94,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's take the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:21.32,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, you heard what \NI said at the peak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I didn't hear nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Ah! You definitely heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I said I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Just leave it at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:34.59,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Still, it's a fact that my \Nreckless comment hurt Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,She's been working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:43.47,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,And I'm the one who gave Ichika the idea\Nto do this, too... during our family trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.18,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You're right. It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.43,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Consider the time and place\Nbefore saying something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.44,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So you did hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I mean, I knew, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.86,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You knew? You knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:00.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,M-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:06.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,that Miku has had feelings for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Am I hearing things?\NCould you say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Stop it! I'm not saying it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.96,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san} the Dense...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well, a lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:23.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So I was really confused when she,\Nof all people, said she was cheering "us" on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.01,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That wasn't really Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I was right about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I said, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You worry about people too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,To be honest, you take it way too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.15,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:44.41,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Remember I told you before about how\Nwhen I failed, everyone came with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.41,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I dragged them all into my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.29,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's not something I can make up for so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:55.67,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's only natural that they \Nshould end up happier than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Is that how it has to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.30,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I wanted everyone to enjoy this trip, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:07.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Is there any way everyone \Ncan be happy, Uesugi{**-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.18,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.10,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,If each person could feel happy without\Ncomparing themselves to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.94,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That would be the kind of \Nworld that you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.74,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:21.94,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:28.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,In reality, it's not uncommon for someone's\Nhappiness to make someone else unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:34.08,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Some kinds of happiness are gained only \Nby competing and taking from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.46,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,In that case, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.46,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There's a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a little presumptuous?\NTrying to get everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.85,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,When you choose to have something, \Nyou choose not to have something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.10,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Someday, you'll have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.27,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Someday, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.52,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.77,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're being tailed by a sneak photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.70,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I noticed it ever since \Nwe were at Kyoto Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.03,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:10.87,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I read in the news that they \Ntarget students on school trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.41,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Even then, why would they target you, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}that{\i0} supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.25,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.00,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,It's a feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.12,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,Let's post it on Instagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:24.67,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Anyway, Miku and Ichika are \Nback at the hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.59,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.09,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Both of them seem worn out\Nafter all that walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.51,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,They're resting in our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:33.02,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I doubt they're in the same room together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I can't believe Miku set out on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.52,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm going to go check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.64,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.90,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm almost done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.44,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.77,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Nino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.91,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Hey, Uesugi{**-kun}, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What happened to Maeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.04,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,A long bathroom visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Me too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.50,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Which means I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.79,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku, Ichika, I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.42,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.64,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,They aren't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.18,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,They're ignoring their phones, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.72,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Miku, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.93,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:17.02,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,But there are still two more \Ndays on the school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.73,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I want you to let me make things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.48,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Yotsuba didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.81,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:32.16,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,After what you said, Nino,\Nnow I'm hearing things, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.74,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're just hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.24,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd be in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.88,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.05,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.31,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Nino, what was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.89,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You finally picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:02.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.90,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}, I'm glad I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.48,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Do you have time tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku, do you have any plans for tomorrow?
Comment: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,{\t(2160,3200,\c&H000000&)}There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Comment: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.36,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,{\an8\t(2160,3200,\c&H000000&)}There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.41,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.00,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You can see all the way to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.90,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What if we fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.29,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It feels higher, seeing it for \Nthe first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.01,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:30.42,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I thought you were with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.80,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanted to talk to Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I thought she'd be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.81,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Miku isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.06,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.73,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,She's resting at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:48.19,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,And Ichika and Nino are walking around \Nwith their friends from second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.61,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Miku, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so the two of us \Nare spending our time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's kind of sad seeing less than half of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.62,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I-It's not bad, for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.83,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, we're at Kiyomizu Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:01.83,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:04.33,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Look at this scenery, Uesugi{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.63,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.80,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Quit tugging!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.96,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You're afraid of {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.21,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,And you call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.60,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I-I'm not scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.84,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You must be freaking out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.43,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.10,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Let's take a picture together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:21.67,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.23,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:23.31,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.98,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Please, Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.23,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.31,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.15,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.99,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why am I being so bold?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:42.04,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But this ought to be enough to make him \Nremember what happened six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.87,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.58,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you have to spend \Nyour school trip like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.29,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm going to rest in my room\Nfor a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.55,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Sure... Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.72,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,There's been a sneak photographer\Nspotted in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.76,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:04.89,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,"Like the shadows, unknowable," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.35,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Imitating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.06,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,In more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:14.61,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,They wouldn't buy that two sisters \Nare both staying in sick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.37,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,When's the next head count?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.37,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm asking why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.71,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:25.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.16,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,If you came to cheer me up, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.04,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.05,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why would I do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.83,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,My rival just backed down by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:42.89,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's nothing but lucky for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.48,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,All I need to do now is defeat Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.85,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,That sly fox...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.60,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What should I do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm taking Fu{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.34,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,"Fu{**-kun}"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.15,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Since when have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.60,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.70,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell me you aren't going \Nto give him up because you liked him first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.66,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Sure, you might have been first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:11.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I don't really know enough to \Nsay time doesn't matter in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.42,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:18.92,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I have no idea what's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:23.05,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,All I know is that I love him\Nmore than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:26.06,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I haven't given up, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.73,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,The school trip is a perfect \Nchance to get close to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're spending it locked in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.44,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You've practically given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.95,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Your turn's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:38.82,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Bye, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.20,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I don't want to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.86,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,But I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.16,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I knew it would end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:49.75,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,But now that Futaro knows how I feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm good enough for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:55.71,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There's no way he would like someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:22:00.84,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I never thought it would be \Nso scary to fight fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:02.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Look, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.59,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Good luck charms for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.27,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's buy one for Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.72,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Um... Where's Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.60,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,He must have gone back to his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:15.23,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.18,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.07,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:23.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You have to tell Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:28.95,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That you were the one who \Nmet him six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.67,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(586,0)}"Sisters War: Part 2."
